<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="punctual-adj">punctual <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'pʌŋktʃuəl/    美 /'pʌŋktʃuəl/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-on-time">1.★ <strong>准时的；守时的：(on time)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Being punctual for classes was essential; no one was allowed to be late.
按时到校上课是最基本的要求，任何人都不允许迟到。</p><footer>外研⑦ – 2</footer></div></div>